channel.title: How did RSPS come about?
channel.description:
This is probably a dumb question but I'm going to ask it anyway.
How did people like WinterLove get Jagex's items and stuff? Like how is everything to scale and what not? Is there some way to rip off all of RuneScape's items and maps? I think it has to do with the cache but I just want to understand it fully..
Sorry if its a stupid question.. :(

item.title: How did RSPS come about?
item.dc:creator: @Odd_Fortune Odd Fortune
item.description:
@Odd_Fortune wrote:

RiiPiiNFtW:

Winterlove was originally created for testing bots. The cache now a days is much different then what it is now so it was much easier.

Ohh I see.

Thanks for answering.
